column5: Before we give out the prizes tomorrow, were going to be doing some additional fund raising when I auction off some great stuff!!  We are still sorting out what we will auction off. We have some really good stuff. Ill have my laptop so Cash is good, but I should be able to take credit cards via PayPal as well.  The one thing I do have here is a box of stuff from Dave Mercer.    The autographed reel is one I think he used on his show, and its a Shimano Chronarch 50 mg.. Im not a baitcaster guy.. but I think its a really good reel!!!!
Fish Farmer will be bringing this up for me TJ.     Frontier 5' 6" Ultra Light I hope somebody will think it the perfect perch rod.
what time will the auctions be starting tomorrow?
last fish measured at 1 p.m so it will be between one and two oclock i imagine!!
Hey TJ.Is the middle pic, one lot to bid on?
Yup.. everything all at once, plus the reel!!
Off to the bank machine in the AM.
